{"tid":1130680,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係咪民粹成風？","createTime":"2019-04-29T08:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T15:03:38.000Z","uid":1301,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c74fb1cf4dda7e35f08ec10c8c9817580dfad2","tid":1130680,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"民粹就我睇黎只係一種手段 並唔係理念<br />\n你可以有左派民粹 右派民粹<br />\n但民粹最重要個樣野就係 pure people vs corrupted elites<br />\n亦即係非我類者 全部都係敵人 所以批鬥是必須的<br />\n呢樣野係極右入面（本土）日日發生<br />\n日日都話人係鬼 例如最近盧仇個單 <br />\n雖然話民粹係可以煽動公眾情感去參與社會活動<br />\n但同時傷害咗成個右派嘅cohesion<br />\n到底 呢仲批鬥方式仲應唔應該繼續？<br />\n最重要嘅係 本土嘅內鬥 真係有咁嘅必要？"},{"pid":"d518dc3ae73a7995d5ef4a86d9eb2783204c55ef","tid":1130680,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"唔係香港，<br />\n<br />\n係兩登仔同本土派入面啫<br />\n<br />\n佔全部人比例唔高"},{"pid":"2b70cfc471a4c05e4b5862f793ab1b621e95c578","tid":1130680,"uid":1301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d518dc3ae73a7995d5ef4a86d9eb2783204c55ef","tid":1130680,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"唔係香港，<br />\n<br />\n係兩登仔同本土派入面啫<br />\n<br />\n佔全部人比例唔高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"你岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一邊屌人唔支持本土<br />\n一邊屌其他本土派 <br />\n真係人唔笑狗到吠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e64ecb7bcdc86766b0355abbb696bcd1194c4a","tid":1130680,"uid":154872,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b70cfc471a4c05e4b5862f793ab1b621e95c578","tid":1130680,"uid":1301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d518dc3ae73a7995d5ef4a86d9eb2783204c55ef","tid":1130680,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"唔係香港，<br />\n<br />\n係兩登仔同本土派入面啫<br />\n<br />\n佔全部人比例唔高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019